title: Single Cozy Room for Rent!
posting_body: ['Features:', '- Shared kitchen, with a fridge, stove, microwave, and many cabinets for storage', '- Large shared living room with plenty of daylight', "- Right on the M-Line, perfect for people who don't mind the noise", '- About 10 minutes away from SFSU by public transit', '- Personal bathroom', '- Full year lease, students welcome!', '- No pets allowed, not furnished.', '- Utilities (electricity, water, waste, internet) provided, but not included in rent (~$100/month)', '- Nearby laundromat, right down the street', 'If you\'re interested, please email me with "Broad" somewhere in the title or body.', 'Include in your email a bit about yourself.', 'Please have your credit score and any references available.', 'Let me know a time we can show you the place, preferably around 10am any weekday or weekend!']
